    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deo Mercurio <expan><abbr>sign</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>ex voto <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Gallicus <lb n="3"/>et <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elia</ex></expan> Sibulla <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuerunt</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibentes</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aeti</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Erhalten waren die Basis und die Beine des Gottes mit einem liegenden Ziegenbock.</p>
            </div>
